---
<section class="cta-section">
  <div class="cta-glow"></div>
  <span class="reveal label">Let's Go</span>
  <h2 class="reveal">Ready to stop losing<br>customers to a <span class="serif">bad</span> website?</h2>
  <p class="reveal">Book a free 15-minute call. I'll audit your current site, show you what you're missing, and give you a clear plan — whether you hire me or not.</p>
  <div class="reveal"><a href="/contact" class="btn-primary">Book Your Free Call <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/></svg></a></div>
  <div class="reveal cta-note">Free audit · No pressure · 15 minutes</div>
</section>
<style>
  .cta-section{padding:120px 24px;text-align:center;position:relative;overflow:hidden}
  .cta-glow{position:absolute;top:50%;left:50%;transform:translate(-50%,-50%);width:500px;height:500px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--pop);opacity:0.04;filter:blur(100px);pointer-events:none}
  .cta-section h2{font-size:clamp(2.2rem,5vw,3.4rem);letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin:12px 0 16px;position:relative;z-index:2}
  .cta-section p{font-size:16px;color:var(--text-dim);max-width:520px;margin:0 auto 32px;line-height:1.7;position:relative;z-index:2}
  .cta-note{font-size:12px;color:var(--text-muted);margin-top:14px;position:relative;z-index:2}
</style>
